metadata.comments: A lightweight framework to implement Model-View-ViewModel applications in WPF, Windows Store, Windows Phone, Silverlight, Xamarin.
Extras components to implement Model-View-ViewModel applications in WPF, Windows Store, Windows Phone, Silverlight, Xamarin.

Platform components to implement Model-View-ViewModel applications in WPF, Windows Store, Windows Phone, Silverlight and Xamarin. These are needed because of technical constraints with portable class libraries (PCL).
Json.NET is a popular high-performance JSON framework for .NET
A simple facade that provides insulation from specific IoC containers.
